name: CURRENTS
description:
The base of the collection. This diamond encrusted, yellow gold chain necklace is modelled after a timeless design and is physically viable, with 3D printing files available. 

Collectors of the 'CURRENTS' work will be given the opportunity to have a customised, one-of-one pendant created, to compliment the chain design. 

Inspired by American and European artistic traditions, BEAUREGARD creates unique digital jewellery pieces that blend state-of-the-art 3D modelling techniques with classic jewellery motifs and gemstones. All artworks are physically viable, and grant collectors exclusive access to custom made additions and modifications.
